        * updated
      Fedora/*.service
        * moved service files to systemd/
    - gateway/obi2ncid.pl:
        * changed: $ncidname = "NONAME" if !$ncidname;
          to:      $ncidname = "NO NAME" if !$ncidname;
      gateway/wc2ncid.pl:
